namespace Health

features
	Health {abstract}
		mandatory
			PatientRecord {abstract}
				mandatory
					Demographics
				optional
					MedicalHistory {abstract}
						or
							Allergies
							ChronicConditions
							FamilyHistory
			Treatment {abstract}
				alternative
					Medication
					Surgery
					Therapy
		optional
			Insurance {abstract}
				alternative
					Public
					Private
			Monitoring

constraints
	Surgery => Private
	ChronicConditions => Monitoring
	FamilyHistory => Insurance